19    /**
20    * Class that defines API used by {@link ObjectMapper} and
21    * {@link JsonSerializer}s to obtain serializers capable of serializing
22    * instances of specific types; as well as the default implementation
23    * of the functionality.
24    *<p>
25    * Provider handles caching aspects of serializer handling; all construction
26    * details are delegated to {@link SerializerFactory} instance.
27    *<p>
28    * Object life-cycle is such that an initial instance ("blueprint") is created
29    * and referenced by {@link ObjectMapper} and {@link ObjectWriter} intances;
30    * but for actual usage, a configured instance is created by using
31    * a create method in sub-class
32    * {@link com.fasterxml.jackson.databind.ser.DefaultSerializerProvider}.
33    * Only this instance can be used for actual serialization calls; blueprint
34    * object is only to be used for creating instances.
35    */
